Lyrics:

There lived a certain man in Russia long ago
He was big and strong, in his eyes a flaming glow
Most people looked at him with terror and with fear
But to Moscow chicks he was such a lovely dear
He could preach the bible like a preacher
Full of ecstasy and fire
But he also was the kind of teacher
Women would desire

RA RA RASPUTIN
Lover of the Russian queen
There was a cat that really was gone
RA RA RASPUTIN
Russia's greatest love machine
It was a shame how he carried on

He ruled the Russian land and never mind the Czar
But the kasachok he danced really wunderbar
In all affairs of state he was the man to please
But he was real great when he had a girl to squeeze
For the queen he was no wheeler dealer
Though she'd heard the things he'd done
She believed he was a holy healer
Who would heal her son

RA RA RASPUTIN
Lover of the Russian queen
There was a cat that really was gone
RA RA RASPUTIN
Russia's greatest love machine
It was a shame how he carried on

But when his drinking and lusting and his hunger
For power became known to more and more people
The demands to do something about this outrageous
Man became louder and louder

"This man's just got to go!" declared his enemies
But the ladies begged "Don't you try to do it, please"
No doubt this Rasputin had lots of hidden charms
Though he was a brute they just fell into his arms
Then one night some men of higher standing
Set a trap, they're not to blame
"Come to visit us" they kept demanding
And he really came

RA RA RASPUTIN
Lover of the Russian queen
They put some poison into his wine
RA RA RASPUTIN
Russia's greatest love machine
He drank it all and he said "I feel fine"

RA RA RASPUTIN
Lover of the Russian queen
They didn't quit, they wanted his head
RA RA RASPUTIN
Russia's greatest love machine
And so they shot him till he was dead

Oh, those Russians...


#BoneyM #Rasputin

snippet.title: STRANGER THINGS 5 SEASON FINALE TRAILER (2025) | Netflix
snippet.description:
#Netflix #StrangerThings #StrangerThings5

🎥 Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
The Stranger Things Season 5 season finale trailer delivers an emotional and explosive first look at the end of the journey as the Stranger Things 5 Final Season reaches its climax on Netflix. The Stranger Things Season 5 official teaser and trailer 2 tease an all-out showdown with Vecna, as Eleven, Mike, Dustin, Lucas, Will, Max, Hopper, Joyce, and Steve face impossible choices to save Hawkins and the world. Featuring the return of Millie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, Noah Schnapp, Sadie Sink, David Harbour, Winona Ryder, and Jamie Campbell Bower, the Stranger Things Season 5 Trailer promises a powerful, heartbreaking, and unforgettable conclusion to the iconic series.

The inspiration behind this video:
The end of the Upside Down is finally here! In this video, we break down the explosive Stranger Things Season 5 Trailer , analyzing every hidden detail in the Stranger Things 5 Final Season trailer 2 . As Netflix prepares to release the massive conclusion to its global phenomenon, the stakes have never been higher for Hawkins. We discuss what the footage reveals about the Stranger Things Final Season trailer 2 and the ultimate war against Vecna ( Jamie Campbell Bower ). Whether you are searching for the Stranger Things Season 5 release date specifics or just reacting to the intense Stranger Things trailer , this video is your ultimate guide to the final chapter.

The entire cast returns for this emotional farewell. We explore the pivotal roles of Millie Bobby Brown ( Eleven ) and Noah Schnapp ( Will Byers ) as they face their destiny in the Stranger Things 5 Official Teaser . We also dive into the fates of Max ( Sadie Sink ), Mike Wheeler ( Finn Wolfhard ), Dustin ( Gaten Matarazzo ), and Lucas ( Caleb McLaughlin ). With Chief Hopper ( David Harbour ) and Joyce Byers ( Winona Ryder ) reunited, the adults including Cara Buono are ready to fight alongside the older teens: Steve Harrington ( Joe Keery ), Nancy Wheeler ( Natalia Dyer ), Jonathan Byers ( Charlie Heaton ), and Robin ( Maya Hawke ).

Finally, we address the massive rumors surrounding the release format. We speculate on the Stranger Things Season 5 Volume 2 trailer and whether the show will have a split release like the previous season. We analyze search trends for Stranger Things Season 5 Part 2 trailer and Stranger Things 5 Volume 2 , discussing what the st5 trailer leaks about the ending. If you follow us you won't want to miss our theory on the Stranger Things 5 trailer volume 2 leaks. Don't miss our full reaction to the st5 trailer and our predictions for the Stranger Things final trailer.

snippet.title: STRANGER THINGS Season 5 FINALE Trailer Explained
snippet.description:
I review, breakdown and explain Stranger Things Season 5 Volume 3 Trailer. I give my reaction to the new official preview for the finale, episode 8 and the ending of the show. I discuss the new clips in the promo which showed Vecna going after Hopper,  Kali betraying Eleven, a character's death, The Abyss merging with The Upside Down, Operation Beanstalk taking place, and Steve and Hopper's potential death. I give my theories and predictions on if Dimension X will be destroyed, if The Mind Flayer will return, it's connection to The First Shadow stage play and other characters such as Mike, Will, Lucas, Max, Joyce, Jonathan, Nancy, Mr Clarke, Robin, Murray, Holly and how the the finale will end.

Rhaenyra Targaryen moves to claim her father’s crown, driven by conviction, prophecy, and the growing belief that only bloodshed can secure her family’s survival, even as that path threatens to reshape her into a far darker ruler. Alicent Hightower grapples with the consequences of ambition and loyalty as former alliances fracture beyond repair, while Daemon Targaryen commits fully to a war that will define his legacy. As dragons, armies, and rival claimants converge, the season marks the true beginning of the civil war that will devastate Westeros, dismantle the Targaryen dynasty from within, and set history on a tragic, irreversible course.

snippet.title: Shrinking — Season 3 Official Trailer | Apple TV
snippet.description:
Moving forward, together. Shrinking Season 3 premieres January 28 on Apple TV https://apple.co/_Shrinking

Shrinking follows a grieving therapist (Jason Segel) who starts to break the rules and tell his clients exactly what he thinks. Ignoring his training and ethics, he finds himself making huge, tumultuous changes to people’s lives...including his own.

Shrinking stars Emmy-Award nominee Jason Segel and Multi-Award winner Harrison Ford, and was created by Emmy Award winners Bill Lawrence and Brett Goldstein (“Ted Lasso”) and Segel. Additional stars include Emmy-Award nominee Christa Miller, Emmy-Award nominee Jessica Williams, Luke Tennie, Michael Urie, Lukita Maxwell, and Ted McGinley. 

Song: “Mr. Miracle” by Kid Cudi https://music.apple.com/us/album/mr-miracle/1825252381?i=1825252384
